Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.40,0:00:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找吧  收集梦想的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.57,0:00:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无奈也能感受到此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.55,0:00:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外表看起来更单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.42,0:00:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法坦诚表达心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.06,0:00:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把想说的话收藏在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.40,0:00:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今更不能说出幼稚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.70,0:00:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好说时间能解决一切 却怕无人能懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.24,0:00:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天24小时我都相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.48,0:00:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.25,0:01:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这是司空见惯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.29,0:01:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间总是嘲笑着匆匆而过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.40,0:01:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其执着回忆 不如寻找现在的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.33,0:01:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.64,0:01:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第58话\N一切源自桃源乡之夜  后篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.85,0:02:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.86,0:02:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.39,0:02:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死胖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.33,0:02:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是半妖吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杀要剐就快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.23,0:02:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半妖的妖力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.63,0:02:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该也能当作人面果的养分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜你之赐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让长生不老的果实\N早日腌渍成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.84,0:02:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以快点恢复妖力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管闹  尽管闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荆棘扎得愈深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就愈容易吸收到养分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.08,0:02:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.56,0:02:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.92,0:02:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇装四魂碎片的小瓶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死胖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那四魂碎片的主人怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.60,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人?我哪知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是捡到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.81,0:02:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装蒜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从戈薇身上抢来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.15,0:03:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有四魂碎片的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到好消息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.32,0:03:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房子的某处有女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人也是人面果最喜欢的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愈年轻愈好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  我马上就来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前千万别被抓到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡到四魂碎片的是这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的箱庭里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.32,0:03:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇!我这边已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底想要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.21,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.24,0:04:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过人面果一定会很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是仙人  桃果人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是好日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀奇的半妖与年轻的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时送上门来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子长生不老的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就可以结果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到了犬夜叉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他出什么事我绝不饶你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇真的好厉害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能冷静的跟他说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她已经见怪不怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了  让你睡一觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.73,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我的手都满是泥巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.94,0:05:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最痛恨这个没用的人类身体了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  流太多血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视线模糊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还活着吧  半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇的衣服  难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你弄坏了我的葫芦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄取养分变的要花很多功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄取养分?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死胖子  你居然把戈薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.54,0:06:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你喜欢上了\N那脏兮兮的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.55,0:06:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上让你们在我的肚子里见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会变成长生不老的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我吃进肚子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饶不了你  死胖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些荆棘的根绝对扯不断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.50,0:06:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么小的身体能吸到什么程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.09,0:07:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘在下面的楼层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.91,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股甜甜的气味是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.64,0:08:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不过是擦伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然变得破破烂烂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是穿上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是人类的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还这么逞强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.67,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我们也在这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不让你们逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉被扁得好惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.69,0:08:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量不要移动比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走得动吗  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面…还没白天吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.84,0:09:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一片黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你还想打吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.47,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妖力恢复之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非逃跑不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到天亮之前  由我保护大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.26,0:09:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跳下去果然太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师与七宝\N也必须要先恢复原来的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.77,0:09:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就这么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都还没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算叫我一个人先逃跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是从箱庭里逃出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷您是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来真丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.49,0:09:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经是桃果人的师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说  老爷爷也是仙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.00,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭老头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么\N让那死胖子修炼成仙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.17,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那家伙变成仙人的不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人面果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人面果?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个月前的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天光是修行  真不想再继续了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.82,0:10:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有马上变成仙人的方法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是食物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是人面果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.08,0:10:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得到仙人的力量吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.02,0:10:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就吃下我人面果的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.06,0:11:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  吃下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.96,0:11:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能和我一同修得仙术了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.06,0:11:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  连籽也吞下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.17,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能得到仙人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.04,0:11:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一吃下人面果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.04,0:11:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心智就会受人面果支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.25,0:11:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是桃果人仿佛被命令般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了结出长生不老的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我做成人面果的肥料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  仙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您现在的样子是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了长生不老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有果实是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须把果实熬成长生不老药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.26,0:11:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而知道方法的只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.57,0:11:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才让你用这样子活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.41,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有本事逃到这地方来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂碎片的威力增强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.58,0:12:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃果人已经不是人类了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.65,0:12:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们收拾掉他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.15,0:12:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我已经不是人类了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类不就是脏兮兮的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后年纪大了等死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸老妈就是这样死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想要\N这种脆弱的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这根本就不是强悍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲别人只为了自己\N长命百岁的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆  我很强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强的人就能利用脆弱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.45,0:12:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连这一点都不懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.69,0:12:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人面果给予脆弱的我强悍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.76,0:12:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我成为最强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.97,0:12:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一定能永远活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱的家伙就当肥料吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你不能乱动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.65,0:13:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这家伙讲道理是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.79,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最了解人类身体的脆弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.59,0:13:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与想要变强的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我看到你就觉得恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在对我说教吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连站都站不起来的软脚虾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这死胖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有资格说我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.81,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这怪物融入四魂碎片之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人面果的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.36,0:13:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他喝一口这种药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是桃果人制作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老之秘药的赝品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.77,0:14:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对治疗伤口立刻就能见效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是喝下它之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会受人面果的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  不要吃果实就没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  想得救的话就喝下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝就喝没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.36,0:14:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多点精神打起来才好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人面果是拿人类当肥料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.43,0:14:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要喝这种会让人恶心的药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.07,0:14:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我和你混为一谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半妖  你不喝下这种药的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会后悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不喝这种鬼东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会输给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.83,0:15:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.76,0:15:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有嘴巴厉害而已吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的身体根本没希望嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.81,0:15:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我现在的身体\N施展风穴大概也无效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.48,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓箭是杀不死桃果人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以打倒他的  绝对!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从弓箭散发破魔之气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位姑娘…到底是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃果人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.74,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败战武士的弓会有什么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.65,0:15:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.83,0:16:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你一定要除掉桃果人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.34,0:16:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样勉强能让我赎罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.65,0:16:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成弓箭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.91,0:16:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙人老爷爷用尽最后的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你大卸八块
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使透过背后也能看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是四魂碎片的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要贯穿那道光的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.92,0:17:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂碎片被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  老爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.10,0:17:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.34,0:17:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.32,0:17:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.06,0:17:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种人类的身体  你也会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.40,0:17:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只要戈薇还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人面果  你是来救我的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想让重要的肥料溜掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.53,0:18:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于得到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.88,0:18:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自由行动的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还得到这么多四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来我就是最强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和我合为一体吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  天总算亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要连半妖的身体也弄到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.65,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我就能为所欲为了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别作梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧  桃果人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.02,0:19:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  妖树人面果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说八道  半妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.17,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招  风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.19,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.50,0:20:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  恢复了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是桃果人的死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让妖术解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.24,0:20:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭里的那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该也恢复原貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃果人死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉也是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.55,0:20:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉掉下去时天色还很暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔日还没有天亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能…就那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉死掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.53,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他已经受了那么重的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.60,0:20:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是以人类的身体\N从这种峭壁坠落的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.37,0:20:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起供养他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.88,0:20:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉也算达成心愿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.25,0:20:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他\N不惜舍命也救了戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.32,0:21:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不觉得高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.32,0:21:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明没有妖力\N还这么勉强自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋  犬夜叉是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了不就什么都没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.37,0:21:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后要怎么办啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.34,0:21:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.91,0:21:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错!犬夜叉是大笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.04,0:21:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着你们不管\N就在那里胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.85,0:21:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.85,0:21:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.62,0:21:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得你应该不会那么轻易就死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.39,0:21:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪会那么容易就挂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做无谓的担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.67,0:21:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫做无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心你是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.81,0:21:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道你会奋不顾身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.61,0:21:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没事不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.58,0:21:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.61,0:21:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有哭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明在哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.58,0:22:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.12,0:22:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.62,0:22:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.32,0:22:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭了\N没有哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.25,0:22:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭了\N没有哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.35,0:22:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭了\N吵死了  坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.66,0:22:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真的挂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.77,0:22:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了真正重要的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.91,0:22:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能舍弃其他一切就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.29,0:22:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而现实却是残酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.43,0:22:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的时刻只要随时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.37,0:22:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.97,0:23:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑海浮现你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.65,0:23:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-但愿直到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.19,0:23:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远沉睡的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.46,0:23:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.93,0:23:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不止息存在我心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.79,0:23:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.02,0:23:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在的这几天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人感觉度日如年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.43,0:23:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.03,0:23:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在驱魔师的村子\N有人想成为你的徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.00,0:23:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们说希望你传授\N驱除妖怪的方法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.80,0:24:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是一对美少女姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.43,0:24:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人羡慕…不  似乎很辛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.44,0:24:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.77,0:24:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美少女姐妹花拜师学艺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.28,0:24:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.71,0:24:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.44,0:24:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.75,0:24:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是臀部而已…



